Architecture: amd64
Maintainer: Loxia AI <support@loxia.ai>
Homepage: https://loxia.ai
Description: Local-first multi-agent AI system for software development
 OnBuzz Community is an open-source local-first autonomous AI agent system
 that empowers developers with intelligent coding assistance.
 .
 Features:
  - Multi-agent orchestration
  - 18+ specialized tools
  - Web UI + CLI interfaces
  - Code analysis and refactoring
  - Task management system
 .
 Commands:
  - onbuzz web: Start server and open Web UI
  - onbuzz terminal: Start Terminal UI
  - onbuzz serve: Start server only (headless)
